                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The spinesnapper makes a claw or weapon Strike. If it hits, in addition to dealing damage, the creature must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:22] saving throw, with the following effects.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected and the spinesnapper is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] until the start of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is pushed 10 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is pushed 10 feet and knocked @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone].</p>"
