                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The spinesnapper has a creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed] or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Restrained]</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The spinesnapper slams the creature against a nearby surface. The target and the surface struck each take @Damage[4d6[bludgeoning]] damage, and the target must succeed at a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:22|traits:damaging-effect] save or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned] for 1 round on a critical failure.</p>"
